eMac for E 0.16
<font face=Chicago/12 color=#ffffff>
<br>
<br>
Welcome to eMac for Enlightenment 0.16. This is a complete MacOS 8.x-like theme.
eMac is very feature rich, with everything from the MacBar to a full widget set.
This theme fully supports Enlightenment version 0.16, with epplet and Eterm automode
support.
<br>
<br>
View the _eMac_Documentation(contents)<br>
<p align=50%>
Visit my web site for backgrounds, icons, and more. Also visit my site for tutorials on writing your own themes for Enlightenment.
<br>
<br>
<font face=Chicago/15 color=#ffffff>
http://www.geocities.com/<br>researchtriangle/thinktank/2631






