<font face=Chicago/20 color=#ffffff>
<br>
Credits
<font face=Chicago/12 color=#ffffff>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<p align=50%>
eMac was written by me, Archon (Jon Rista). The images used for the MacBar and the
default window borders were copied from a few screenshots I took of MacOS 8.5. All
other images for the widgets, epplets, etc. were created by me. The boot background
and the official eMac background were created by me.
<br>
<br>
A big thanks for all the fans who have helped me with ideas and by sending me "bug"
reports. I appreciate all the help. :)
<br>
<br>
Also a big thanks to Apple Computer, Inc. for such a great-looking idea. :)
